  "text": "What was the reason for the wandering of these two Wanderers, and were they male and female? I am Ra. All Wanderers come to be of assistance in serving the Creator, each in its own way. The Wanderers of which we have been speaking were indeed incarnated male and female as this is by far the most efficient system of partnership.",
